Ing State a Pisanmetung a '''Serbia at Montenegro''' ({{lang-sr|Државна заједница '''Србија и Црна Гора''' / Državna zajednica '''Srbija i Crna Gora'''}}, abbreviated as СЦГ / ''SCG''), metung yang [[confederation|confederasyun]] a [[Political union|pisanmetung]] a '''[[Serbia]]''' at '''[[Montenegro]]''', nung nu atiu inyang 2003 at 2006. Deng aduang republica, pareu lang dating republica ning [[Socialist Federal Republic of Yugoslavia|SFR Yugoslavia]], a dati mitatag bilang ing [[Federal Republic ning Yugoslavia]] inyang [[1992]]. Inyang [[2003]], ing FRY me meyalilan ya pangabuu bilang a State Pisanmetung a Serbia at Montenegro.
